wikipedia_page.main: Harry John Swindells (born 21 February 1999) is an English cricketer. He made his List A debut for Leicestershire in the 2018 Royal London One-Day Cup on 7 June 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Leicestershire in the 2018 t20 Blast on 3 August 2018. He made his first-class debut on 3 June 2019, for Leicestershire in the 2019 County Championship.
